SureVoIP,is,an,internet,telephony,service,provider,supplying,hosted,VoIP,solutions,SIP,trunks,inbound,numbers,and,other,related,VoIP,products,and,services,in,the,UK,The,SureVoIP,API,lets,users,automate,their,interaction,with,the,SureVoIP,platforms,With,the,API,developers,can,create,scripts,applications,or,mashups,which,can,create,customers,send,SMS,messages,and,faxes,search,numbers,provision,numbers,generate,VoIP,calls,manage,accounts,and,more,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML,JSON,Text,and,HTML,and,others